 Proto1000 waited very patiently for the decepticons to arrive. he shifted 
into diffrent forms. He sudden;ly turned into the human know as Rhichard 
Nixon. A squirll looked at him funn. "What are you lookin at?" he said in 
that classic tone. He turned into the original Optimus Prime. "Im big red and 
ill kick your waste desposal unit." He went to pure luquid. And looked at his 
reflection off his body. "I can see myself." He looked back up and waited 
still.

  Archon waited outside the maximal cuty. Suddenly he felt a serge of power 
break free from the matrix....this powwer was old and very big. He sent a 
comm to the maximals...."Anytime."
